    "description_full": "The objective of this system is to outperform SPY across most market conditions by employing a systematic long–short equity strategy that captures cross-sectional beta dispersion in U.S. large-cap stocks. Each trading day after the open, the algorithm estimates rolling betas relative to the S&amp;P500 across a broad, liquid universe. It selects a small set of the lowest-beta names for the long sleeve and a set of the highest-beta names for the short sleeve. This configuration enables a repeatable, sustainable return profile driven by persistent dispersion effects and disciplined structure, rather than aggressive sizing or market directionality.\n",
